# 2. Create a new Business App
# 3. Add products: Facebook Login, Instagram Graph API
# 4. Get App ID and App Secret from Dashboard
# 5. Generate a Long-Lived Access Token (60 days)
# 6. Connect your Facebook Page and Instagram Business Account

